text: Renee Ilene Sandstrom (born February 15, 1974), an American singer and actress. She is better known by her stage name, Renee Sands. She is best known for her role as Renee on the 1980s children's television show Kids Incorporated - seasons 0-4 (1983-1987). ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Singers from Massachusetts Category:Actors from Massachusetts
